Package: lvplot
Type: Package
Title: Level value plots for R
Version: 0.1
Author: Heike Hofmann <hofmann@iastate.edu>, Hadley Wickham
    <h.wickham@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Hadley Wickham <hadley@iastate.edu>
Description: This package implements the letter value
    boxplot which extend the standard boxplot to deal with
    both larger and smaller data by dynamically selecting
    the appropriate number of letter values to display.
Depends:
    RColorBrewer
License: MIT
Collate:
    'calculate.r'
    'draw.r'
    'lvbagplot.R'
    'lvplot.r'
